pull_request.title: New ci
pull_request.body:
As agreed with @xvzcf : Several new, Docker-enabled CI images (Ubuntu, Debian, Centos, Alpine). 

Also changed: Removal of 'nist' 'openssl102' testing.

Also added: 'dynamic' and 'static' build type (dynamic default).

Because of these additional things, only creating draft PR.
